Description.Name: Jump...Jump Around...
Description.Details: Sumire is standing over by the Kerby-Fucheatah Console, "Commander, do you want to make any changes to the KF Console while we are orbiting [[TGT_SYSTEM,{TGT_SYSTEM.Name}]]?

Description.Name: Keep KF Console Active
Description.Details: KF Console is ACTIVE

Description.Name: Keep KF Console Active
Description.Details: You ponder her query for a few minutes before responding, "Leave KF Console ACTIVE and we will continue using a Pirate Point for our next jump." The KF Console is currently ACTIVE.

Description.Name: Keep KF Console Inactive
Description.Details: KF Console is INACTIVE

Description.Name: Keep KF Console Inactive
Description.Details: You ponder her query for a few minutes before responding, "Leave KF Console INACTIVE and we will continue using normal travel for our next jump." The KF Console is currently INACTIVE.
